            "EarthSciModels migration (esm-nw73)"
        ],
        "references": [
            {
                "citation": "Seinfeld, J. H., & Pandis, S. N. (2006). Atmospheric Chemistry and Physics: From Air Pollution to Climate Change, 2nd ed. Wiley. Chapter 6 В§6.2, Eqs. 6.5-6.8, pp. 207-212. The NO-NOв‚‚-Oв‚ѓ photochemical cycle, the photostationary-state (Leighton) relationship, the photostationary-state parameter О¦, and the net ozone production rate. Rate constants from Table B.1; j_NO2 typical midday value from Figure 4.x photolysis-rate discussion."
            }
