                {
                    "id": "o3_pss_linear_in_no2_doubled",
                    "description": "Doubled endpoint of the upstream `O3_pss Scales with NO2/NO Ratio` test. With NO2 doubled to 2.0e16 mвЃ»Ві (NO held at 1.0e16, NO2/NO ratio = 2), O3_pss doubles to exactly 8.421052631578948e17 mвЃ»Ві вЂ” exactly 2Г— the baseline 4.210526315789474e17. Pinned at rel=1e-10. Together with `o3_pss_linear_in_no2_baseline` reproduces the upstream linearity assertion O3_pss(2В·NO2) = 2В·O3_pss(NO2), which follows structurally from Eq. 6.6's linear numerator j_NO2В·NO2.",
