                {
                    "id": "clean_remote_low_nox",
                    "description": "Clean-remote regime: NO=2.5e15 mвЃ»Ві (~0.1 ppb), NO2=2.5e15 mвЃ»Ві (~0.1 ppb), O3=7.5e17 mвЃ»Ві (~30 ppb), O2/M at defaults. Exercises all four outputs at the low-NOx end of the tropospheric range. With NO2/NO = 1 the photostationary ozone O3_pss = 4.210526315789474e17 mвЃ»Ві (~17 ppb); the ambient O3 of 30 ppb is above it, so О¦ = 0.561 < 1 and P_O3 = -1.5625e13 mвЃ»Ві/s < 0 (weak net loss). O = 2.54e8 mвЃ»Ві вЂ” two orders of magnitude below the typical-midday O because NO2 is 20Г— smaller. All pinned at rel=1e-10.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {"NO": 2.5e15, "NO2": 2.5e15, "O3": 7.5e17},
